Package de.chojo.sadu.queries.call

Class CallImpl

java.lang.Object
de.chojo.sadu.queries.call.CallImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Call
public final class CallImpl extends Object implements Call
A call is a subelement of a Calls. It represents a single query call of any kind.
